-- LG Says It Will Unveil World's First Smartphone With Dual-Core Processor
-- B y   J u n   Y a n g
-- 2010-12-16T02:07:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-16/lg-says-it-will-unveil-world-s-first-smartphone-with-dual-core-processor.html
LG Electronics Inc. will in January
unveil the world’s first smartphone built with a dual-core
processor, the company said in a statement today. The model,
named “Optimus 2X,” is powered by Google Inc.’s Android
operating system, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
